skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ink tober
des: Inktober is a concept that throughout October, you should do at least one drawing a day. As inspiration of what to draw, there are daily suggestions. This skill will help remind you to draw something and let you know what the daily suggestion is. For more information about inktober, go to https://inktober.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
